[0.0, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H                                                         \u2502 repo     ananta\n    \u2584\u2584\u2584                                                  \u2502 cwd      .\n\u2584\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580                                                  \u2502 git      Krusty  main \u2717\n\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2584                                               \u2502 hub      \u25cf localhost:5000\n\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580                                                \u2502 auth     unset\n \u2580\u2580\u2580  \u2580\u2580\u2580\u2584                                               \u2502 section  dashboard\n                                                         \u2502 mode     normal\n                                                         \u2502 \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[NAV]                  |  DASHBOARD                             |  DETAIL                           \n>  Dashboard           |   System                               |                                   \n . Goals               |     lmstudio   ok                      |   Commands:                       \n . Tasks               |     ollama     unstable                |     :section <id>   switch section\n . Artifacts           |     Queue   4 tasks pending            |     :refresh        reload data   \n . Knowledge           |                                        |     :focus <pane>   nav/content...\n . Config              |   go to Goals or Tasks for details     |     :help           keybindings   \n . System              |                                        |                                   \n . Audit               |                                        |                                   \n . Terminal            |                                        |                                   \n . Help    