[6.0, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H                                                         \u2502 repo     ananta\n    \u2584\u2584\u2584                                                  \u2502 cwd      .\n\u2584\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580                                                  \u2502 git      Krusty  main \u2717\n\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2584                                               \u2502 hub      \u25cf localhost:5000\n\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580\u2580                                                \u2502 auth     unset\n \u2580\u2580\u2580  \u2580\u2580\u2580\u2584                                               \u2502 section  help\n                                                         \u2502 mode     normal\n                                                         \u2502 \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n[NAV]                  |  HELP                                  |  DETAIL                           \n>. Dashboard           |                                        |                                   \n . Goals               | j selection_down Move selection down   |   Commands:                       \n . Tasks               | k selection_up Move selection up       |     :section <id>   switch section\n . Artifacts           | h focus_left Move focus left           |     :refresh        reload data   \n . Knowledge           | l focus_right Move focus right         |     :focus <pane>   nav/content...\n . Config              | gg selection_first Move to first item  |     :help           keybindings   \n . System              | G selection_last Move to last item     |                                   \n . Audit               | / search Open search                   |                                   \n . Terminal            | : command_mode Open command line       |                                   \n*. Help                | r refresh Refresh active section       |                                   \n                       | ? help Toggle help overlay             |                                   \n                       | enter inspect Inspect selected item    |                                   \n                       | q quit Quit operator TUI               |                                   \n                       |                                        |                                   \n                       |                                        |                                   \n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nendpoint=http://localhost:5000 auth=unset focus=navigation mode=normal status=ready mouse_support...\n \n[Tab/\u2190\u2192] Focus  [j/k/\u2191\u2193] Move  [r] Refresh  [n/p] Section  [Enter] Inspect  [e] Inline Vim  [o] M...\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nHELP\nj selection_down Move selection down\nk selection_up Move selection up\nh focus_left Move focus left\nl focus_right Move focus right\ngg selection_first Move to first item\nG selection_last Move to last item\n/ search Open search\n: command_mode Open command line\nr refresh Refresh active section\n? help Toggle help overlay\nenter inspect Inspect selected item\nq quit Quit operator TUI\n"]
